data.description:
Welcome to your future home sweet home! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem, spanning 1,600 square feet, is nestled on a generous .3-acre lot adorned with magnificent mature trees that offer both shade and tranquility. Located in a welcoming community, this property combines the best of both worlds - a peaceful country feel with the convenience of easy commuting to New Braunfels and Seguin.

As you step onto the front porch, you'll immediately be captivated by the picturesque field view that stretches out in front of your new home. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or enjoying a relaxing evening while soaking in the serene countryside scenery.

This home, though in need of a little TLC, is bursting with potential. With a bit of love and creativity, you can transform it into the home of your dreams. The possibilities are endless!
